<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>LUMIER - 프리미엄 뷰티 살롱</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Italiana&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            gold: '#D4AF37',
            cream: '#FDFBF7',
          },
          fontFamily: {
            serif: ['Italiana', 'serif'],
            sans: ['Noto Sans KR', 'sans-serif'],
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-cream text-gray-800 font-sans">

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center bg-cream/90 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-gold/20">
    <div class="text-2xl font-serif tracking-widest">LUMIER</div>
    <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 text-xs tracking-widest">
      <a href="#services" class="hover:text-gold transition">서비스</a>
      <a href="#gallery" class="hover:text-gold transition">갤러리</a>
      <a href="#about" class="hover:text-gold transition">브랜드</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-gold transition">예약</a>
    </div>
    <button onclick="toggleModal()" class="border border-gray-800 px-6 py-2 text-xs hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition uppercase">
      간편 예약
    </button>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero with Enhanced Contrast -->
  <header class="h-screen relative flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600334089648-b0d9d3028eb2?q=80&w=1920" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center text-white space-y-6 animate-fade-in px-4">
      <p class="text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">Premium Beauty Lounge</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-serif tracking-wide drop-shadow-md">
        Timeless <br> <span class="text-gold italic">Elegance</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="font-light text-sm md:text-base tracking-wider max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed opacity-90">
        당신만의 고유한 아름다움을 찾아드립니다. <br>
        최고의 전문가들이 선사하는 럭셔리 뷰티 케어를 경험하세요.
      </p>
      <div class="pt-8">
        <button onclick="toggleModal()" class="bg-white text-black px-8 py-3 text-xs tracking-widest hover:bg-gold hover:text-white transition uppercase">
          스타일 상담하기
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Services Grid -->
  <section id="services" class="py-24 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl mb-4">Our Services</h2>
      <div class="w-10 h-px bg-gold mx-auto"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 text-center">
      <div class="space-y-4 group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleModal()">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-full w-48 h-48 mx-auto mb-6 border-4 border-transparent group-hover:border-gold transition duration-500">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1562322140-8baeececf3df?q=80&w=500" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-700">
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl">Hair Styling</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed px-4">
          최신 트렌드 컷트부터 퍼스널 컬러 염색까지. 
          손상 없는 프리미엄 약제만을 사용합니다.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gold text-sm font-bold">₩35,000 ~</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleModal()">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-full w-48 h-48 mx-auto mb-6 border-4 border-transparent group-hover:border-gold transition duration-500">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1596462502278-27bfdd403348?q=80&w=500" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-700">
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl">Make Up</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed px-4">
          웨딩, 면접, 데이트 등 특별한 날을 위한 메이크업. 
          당신의 장점을 자연스럽게 부각시켜 드립니다.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gold text-sm font-bold">₩80,000 ~</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleModal()">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-full w-48 h-48 mx-auto mb-6 border-4 border-transparent group-hover:border-gold transition duration-500">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1570172619644-dfd03ed5d881?q=80&w=500" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-700">
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl">Spa & Care</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed px-4">
          편안한 휴식과 함께하는 두피 클리닉 및 스킨케어. 
          지친 몸과 마음에 활력을 불어넣으세요.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gold text-sm font-bold">₩50,000 ~</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Reservation Modal -->
  <div id="modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/60 z-[60] hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="bg-cream w-full max-w-md p-8 relative shadow-2xl">
      <button onclick="toggleModal()" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-2xl hover:text-gold">&times;</button>
      
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl mb-2">Reservation</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 tracking-widest uppercase">당신의 아름다움을 예약하세요</p>
      </div>

      <form class="space-y-6" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('예약이 완료되었습니다.'); toggleModal();">
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <label class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">Name</label>
          <input type="text" class="w-full bg-white border border-gray-200 p-3 focus:border-gold outline-none">
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <label class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">Date & Time</label>
          <input type="datetime-local" class="w-full bg-white border border-gray-200 p-3 focus:border-gold outline-none text-gray-500">
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <label class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">Service</label>
          <select class="w-full bg-white border border-gray-200 p-3 focus:border-gold outline-none">
            <option>Hair Cut (₩35,000)</option>
            <option>Dye & Color (₩80,000)</option>
            <option>Perm (₩100,000)</option>
            <option>Make Up (₩80,000)</option>
            <option>Head Spa (₩50,000)</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        
        <button class="w-full bg-black text-white py-4 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest hover:bg-gold transition uppercase">
          Confirm Booking
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function toggleModal() {
      const modal = document.getElementById('modal');
      if(modal.classList.contains('hidden')) {
        modal.classList.remove('hidden');
      } else {
        modal.classList.add('hidden');
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
